A fragrance meant for the day and for the night.. In the end you’ll just know that you made the right choice.. Whether u’ve got one foot at the bar or one foot in the sand..
At Palmbalm our aim is to impart confidence in you whether you’re out day cruising at the beach or out on a night full of fun and mischief. We are a lifestyle fragrance brand based right here in Hawaii. Our products are 100% alcohol and chemical free and made with natural human-grade pheromones and essential oils deriving straight from flowers and fruit trees from these islands.
